OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776729782
OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers relegated from
OL,4,CPremier League
OL,6,FWolverhampton Wanderers have been
OL,7,Fofficially relegated from the Premier
OL,8,FLeague without kicking a ball.
OL,10,FIt's after fellow strugglers West Ham
OL,11,FUnited secured a point against Crystal
OL,12,FPalace in a nil-nil draw on Monday
OL,13,Fnight.
OL,15,FThat means that the side from London,
OL,16,Fwho are managed by the man who brought
OL,17,FWolves into the Premier League, Nuno
OL,18,FEspirito Santo, couldn't be caught.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776729782
OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers relegated from
OL,4,CPremier League
OL,6,FBut, many had been expecting this as
OL,7,FWolves have had a poor season, only
OL,8,Fwinning three league games.
OL,10,FThe club has been rock bottom of the
OL,11,Ftable since week three of the campaign.
OL,13,FThere were fears that the side from
OL,14,Fthe Black Country would break the
OL,15,Frecord for the side with the lowest
OL,16,Fpoints in a Premier League season.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776729782
OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers relegated from
OL,4,CPremier League
OL,6,FBut, after Vitor Pereira was dismissed
OL,7,Fin November last, and former player
OL,8,FRob Edwards came in, Wolves' form
OL,9,Feventually turned around, meaning
OL,10,FDerby County's record of 11 points
OL,11,Fwill stay with them.
OL,13,FHowever, wins against Aston Villa and
OL,14,FLiverpool and a draw against table-
OL,15,Ftopping Arsenal were a little too late
OL,16,Ffor Wolves.
OL,18,FThe early-season dropping of points
OL,19,Fmeans they were too far adrift of the
OL,20,Fteams around them.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776729782
OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers relegated from
OL,4,CPremier League
OL,6,FNow, Rob Edwards will have to see out
OL,7,Fthe remaining five games in the
OL,8,FPremier League before planning for
OL,9,Flife in the Championship.
OL,11,FSomething the fans in old gold haven't
OL,12,Fseen since 2018.
OL,14,FWolves interim executive chairman
OL,15,FNathan Shi wrote a message on the
OL,16,Fclub's website after their relegation.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776729782
OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers relegated from
OL,4,CPremier League
OL,6,FHe said: "Confirmation of our
OL,7,Frelegation is a difficult moment for
OL,8,Feveryone connected to Wolves. While
OL,9,Fthis is a deeply disappointing
OL,10,Foutcome, work has been underway since
OL,11,Fmy arrival in December to ensure we
OL,12,Fare ready to respond with clarity and
OL,13,Fconviction.
OL,15,F"We are clear on what needs to
OL,16,Fimprove, and our focus is now on
OL,17,Fstrengthening the club, building
OL,18,Fmomentum and creating a team our
OL,19,Fsupporters can believe in. We know
OL,20,Fwhat is required and will approach the
OL,21,Fmonths ahead with purpose.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/6
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1776729782
OL,3,CWolverhampton Wanderers relegated from
OL,4,CPremier League
OL,6,F"We know this season has tested your
OL,7,Floyalty and patience. Your backing,
OL,8,Fhome and away, has not been taken for
OL,9,Fgranted. You deserve better and giving
OL,10,Fyou a club you can genuinely be proud
OL,11,Fof is what drives everything we do
OL,12,Ffrom this point forward."
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/6
